snippet.title: Pandemic of the Forgotten Virus Trailer
snippet.description:
Pandemic of the Forgotten Virus is a local multiplayer bullet hell shooter game where 2 players can compete with each other or an AI to try and defeat each other and reach the stratosphere.

Download the game here!
https://eaglescommander.itch.io/pandemic-of-the-forgotten-virus
